{"_id":"lBctmJiL6HgwEIW7","name":"Tier 4 Melee Critical Hits (Levels 13-20)","description":"Critical hit effects for melee attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Legendary effects for legendary adventurers.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"ZrCDE34vfvsoVN4e","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"5Ajy6G5Kpfs6sXna","type":0,"text":"Crippled Arm - Your strike ruins the target's weapon arm. They take -2 to attack rolls until healed with Regenerate or similar magic.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"1a5Z1ukngSVJRaRy","type":0,"text":"Pain Overload - Blinding waves of pain wrack the target. They have disadvantage on all attacks until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Pain Overload","duration":1}}},{"_id":"vH31t1x8RUQvJdpW","type":0,"text":"Rattled - The thunderous impact scatters the target's wits. They have disadvantage on their ability checks until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Rattled","duration":1}}},{"_id":"SmlDlEkcMWU5jbyw","type":0,"text":"Disoriented - Your blow leaves the target's senses swimming. They have disadvantage on all saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Disoriented","duration":1}}},{"_id":"JD6sgeBLxImKqXIA","type":0,"text":"Armor Shattered - Your devastating strike caves in the target's armor. They take -3 AC until it is repaired with smith's tools or magic.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"FAsLaZjf7eJpChDC","type":0,"text":"Sundered Plate - Your blow rips a section of armor away entirely. The target takes -4 AC until it is repaired by a master smith.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-4,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"AFG6kIHpyAiVSIIq","type":0,"text":"Driving Slam - You drive your full weight into the blow. The target must succeed on a DC 17 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"YxHog2HbdHJO7FuJ","type":0,"text":"Mortal Wound - Your strike opens a mortal wound. The target takes three extra weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"O1LPTwxU1SyDL7On","type":0,"text":"Blood in the Eyes - A gout of blood blinds the target. They are blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"uRaFv8gfyZ1BEnVQ","type":0,"text":"Gut Wound - Your blade rips through the target's innards. They must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be poisoned until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"GM46O3nb4649ayS0","type":0,"text":"Pinning Strike - Your weapon hooks the target and pins them in place. They are grappled until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"grappled","duration":1}}},{"_id":"a6Nmu71AfPWBTwqN","type":0,"text":"Hamstrung - Your blade severs the tendons of the target's leg. They are restrained until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"RIUpPdby61szUBVl","type":0,"text":"Completely Exposed - Your strike leaves the target utterly open. Attacks against them have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Completely Exposed","duration":3}}},{"_id":"AcYhykvpUxo2390q","type":0,"text":"Terror Incarnate - Your devastating strike fills the target with dread. They must succeed on a DC 17 Wisdom save or be frightened of you for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":3}}},{"_id":"IbXMjqpwQ0lS7Qm3","type":0,"text":"Disemboweling Strike - Your blade guts the target. They must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be incapacitated until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"incapacitated","duration":1}}},{"_id":"KsS7hiLtYH2Og2dh","type":0,"text":"Overwhelming Power - Your devastating blow lands with crushing force. The target takes four extra weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"GQKfW4L3ysvk7V2n","type":0,"text":"Crippling Wound - Your devastating blow maims a limb. The target has disadvantage on all attack rolls until healed with Regenerate or similar magic.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Crippled Limb","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"C9Qvp8mjTtgPkCvZ","type":0,"text":"Deep Organ Strike - Your blade pierces something vital. The target must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be paralyzed until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"paralyzed","duration":1}}},{"_id":"4I3PjDZaGssbifTP","type":0,"text":"Devastating Strike - Your blow strikes with lethal precision. The target must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or take an extra 6d10 damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"6d10","damageType":"weapon"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392749,"modifiedTime":1783703392749,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"z0HEkABBZK3JQUaR","name":"Tier 4 Melee Fumbles (Levels 13-20)","description":"Fumble effects for melee attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Even legends can fail catastrophically.","img":"icons/skills/melee/strike-sword-slashing-red.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"t8FAym7Xo4zDCfxZ","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - You stumble but recover with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"ZHz9XrXREtjh4O9t","type":0,"text":"Jarred Wrist - You jar your wrist on the botched swing, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"yib5uOBvtYBtN3ZQ","type":0,"text":"Off Your Feet - You lurch off balance and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Off Your Feet","duration":0}}},{"_id":"647ggASBbX5UGBLd","type":0,"text":"Lost Grip - Your weapon twists in your hand. You have disadvantage on your next melee weapon attack.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.mwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Lost Grip","duration":0}}},{"_id":"1pEoy2pzqlAXCL4H","type":0,"text":"Dropped Guard - You drop your guard, taking a -2 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"F9eBMjejvrvT168P","type":0,"text":"Weapon Badly Damaged - Your weapon is badly damaged. You take a -3 penalty to attack rolls until it is repaired.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"aKM1EoH4yDKdHsCc","type":0,"text":"Shaken Confidence - Your failure rattles you to your core. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Shaken Confidence","duration":1}}},{"_id":"HPzrX1g9KkAo7J3g","type":0,"text":"Utterly Exposed - Your catastrophic failure leaves you completely vulnerable. Attacks against you have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Utterly Exposed","duration":3}}},{"_id":"oZ3N5Smqv67Mopr5","type":0,"text":"Severe Self-Injury - You critically wound yourself. Take 3d6 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3d6","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"5ohDp9qf8HpoAvJf","type":0,"text":"Sprawled - Your wild swing throws you off balance and you fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/falling.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"TRdtwjSZiKTFPgSC","type":0,"text":"Ears Ringing - Your own clumsy blow rings your helm like a bell. You are deafened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"deafened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"KKEUhq9BSvCJbUAY","type":0,"text":"Rattled - Your fumble rattles your nerve. You are frightened until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":1}}},{"_id":"bEY1VexVOafhxUCQ","type":0,"text":"Weapon Flung - Your weapon flies from your grasp, landing well out of reach.","img":"icons/svg/sword.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"T0G1bTBjzUo53awo","type":0,"text":"Hit Yourself Critically - Your weapon rebounds and strikes you critically. Take 3d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"HHl3SyFhxUy89r27","type":0,"text":"Concussed Yourself - You crack your own skull with the pommel. You are stunned until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":0}}},{"_id":"ACq36NCa2Vv9Qu05","type":0,"text":"Incapacitated - Your catastrophic failure leaves you reeling. You are incapacitated until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"incapacitated","duration":1}}},{"_id":"Cve6YJ2iIxkPM0d8","type":0,"text":"Blown Wind - The reckless effort leaves you gasping. You gain one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"O0F1BI4sD0Yeu2Nu","type":0,"text":"Devastating Self-Wound - Your weapon rebounds catastrophically. Take 4d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"Mt82ywY6DzLs0tEo","type":0,"text":"Wild Swing - Your uncontrolled swing hits your nearest ally. Roll an attack against that ally's AC; on a hit, deal weapon damage.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}},{"_id":"nBezZCIt67FugPyk","type":0,"text":"Grievous Overswing - You overcommit with legendary force. Make a DC 17 Constitution saving throw or take 4d6 damage and fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"prone","damageFormula":"4d6","damageType":"weapon"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"melee","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392749,"modifiedTime":1783703392749,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"sLrB5Cp5inNEQG9i","name":"Tier 4 Ranged Critical Hits (Levels 13-20)","description":"Critical hit effects for ranged attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Legendary effects for legendary adventurers.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"Pq0Slfek3gTCqgi2","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical strike deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"XnajloIPC0HcBZfB","type":0,"text":"Severed Tendon - Your shot severs a tendon in the target's arm, giving them -2 to attack rolls until they receive healing.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"fNiAIi4gKtJjNQbY","type":0,"text":"Suppressing Shot - A relentless hail of covering fire pins the target down, giving them disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Suppressed","duration":1}}},{"_id":"sDCPL1wglYuJl00n","type":0,"text":"Staggering Shot - Your shot staggers the target completely, giving them disadvantage on attacks and saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.all","save.all"],"effectName":"Staggered","duration":1}}},{"_id":"wU9D4XNXtBif5yei","type":0,"text":"Armor Destroyed - Your shot ruins a section of the target's armor, imposing -4 AC until it is replaced or magically repaired.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-4,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"W6sfWae649oxXyaO","type":0,"text":"Crippling Devastation - Your shot shatters bone after bone, leaving the target with disadvantage on attacks until magically healed.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Crippled","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"gVFXuHC2rVI8a3ue","type":0,"text":"Grit in the Eye - A spray of grit and blood catches the target across the eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"LvsvxJEZX3gqoLYw","type":0,"text":"Completely Exposed - Your shot lays the target's defenses bare, granting advantage on attacks against them for three rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Completely Exposed","duration":3}}},{"_id":"KDw0373PNVO1bo0K","type":0,"text":"Bleeder - The wound opens wide and bleeds freely, dealing an extra 2d6 piercing damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"piercing"}}},{"_id":"cOyqAVxiDcVcWNrB","type":0,"text":"Devastating Impact - Your shot strikes with tremendous force, dealing an extra three weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"vPUnQo3nG8nPD8aX","type":0,"text":"Kneecapped - Your shot shatters the target's knee, forcing a DC 17 Dexterity save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"E6CWAdyJ3jvYzJAc","type":0,"text":"Blinding Strike - Your shot ruins the target's eyes, blinding them until healed by Regenerate or similar magic.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"3bG8uSwrar5XWikP","type":0,"text":"Nailed Down - The projectile nails the target to the ground, leaving them restrained until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"restrained","duration":1}}},{"_id":"jgvhOumGG8rfzQ6P","type":0,"text":"Deep Puncture - Your projectile buries itself deep, dealing an extra maximized weapon die of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1WB","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"rgGjODRgfEep8OFx","type":0,"text":"Sinking Terror - A shot to a vital spot fills the target with dread, forcing a DC 17 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"SLn9LF6biVXYA4lu","type":0,"text":"Overwhelming Shot - Your legendary shot tears through the target, dealing an extra four weapon dice of damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4W","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"ZcqHqmIwikaC4WOd","type":0,"text":"Punctured Lung - Your shot punctures a lung, forcing a DC 17 Constitution save or be poisoned while the target struggles to breathe.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"Dxe5gVLHK5vscKBI","type":0,"text":"Skull Ringer - The impact rattles the target's skull, forcing a DC 17 Constitution save or be stunned until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"stunned"}}},{"_id":"eVLwPpjBr7zfR2XO","type":0,"text":"Crippling Volley - A crippling barrage overwhelms the target's body, inflicting one level of exhaustion until they recover.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"b19NLPqIQ49BIp7l","type":0,"text":"Heart-Piercing Shot - Your shot seeks the heart, forcing a DC 17 Constitution save or take an extra 6d10 damage.","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"6d10","damageType":"piercing"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392749,"modifiedTime":1783703392749,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"GZwSWkTKffCcatWG","name":"Tier 4 Ranged Fumbles (Levels 13-20)","description":"Fumble effects for ranged attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Even legends can fail catastrophically.","img":"icons/weapons/bows/longbow-recurve-brown.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"rjgQEqEJiumSOlyD","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your shot goes wide but you recover with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"f2N7Kxbn4RGSIBwn","type":0,"text":"Watering Eyes - Your eyes water from the effort and you have disadvantage on your next ability check.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"ability.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Watering Eyes","duration":0}}},{"_id":"LsLuTulIJ9PH1p4B","type":0,"text":"Flinch - You flinch at your own misfire and have disadvantage on your next saving throw.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Flinch","duration":0}}},{"_id":"xc90EWrXcZwrDPsA","type":0,"text":"Snapped String - Your bowstring snaps taut awkwardly and you have disadvantage on ranged attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rwak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Snapped String","duration":1}}},{"_id":"al9usnIvuhy4Ay76","type":0,"text":"Fouled Aim - Your aim is thrown off and you have disadvantage on your next attack roll.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Fouled Aim","duration":0}}},{"_id":"b9L4vaOA21CvtKe0","type":0,"text":"Overdrawn - You overdraw and wrench your form, taking a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"xly0ZGTh9stDHGge","type":0,"text":"Recoil Strain - The recoil wrenches your arm; take 1d8 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d8","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"CjQre672eceAfD2F","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Shot - You telegraph your shot and your target has advantage on its next saving throw against you.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Shot","duration":0}}},{"_id":"wYAcKLDEeF8YbLHy","type":0,"text":"Caught Flat - You are caught flat-footed; attacks against you have advantage until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Caught Flat","duration":1}}},{"_id":"j9XwzNP7NTLEubf4","type":0,"text":"Jammed Solid - Your weapon jams solid and you have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Jammed Solid","duration":1}}},{"_id":"X5mwl0NgOht5oPj5","type":0,"text":"Exposed Flank - Your stance collapses, leaving a -3 penalty to your AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-3,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"EUTa32N1JuALSaVA","type":0,"text":"Dropped Weapon - Your ranged weapon flies from your hands, landing 30 feet away.","img":"icons/svg/net.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disarm"}}},{"_id":"JwRaqMWLSJlzmht7","type":0,"text":"Off-Balance - You lose your footing; make a DC 17 Dexterity saving throw or fall prone.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"dex","effectCondition":"prone","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"560TecktReXdvbXD","type":0,"text":"Winded - The strain wracks your body; make a DC 17 Constitution saving throw or take 2d8 bludgeoning damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"2d8","damageType":"bludgeoning"}}},{"_id":"0nJHM67IGeq7APKm","type":0,"text":"Stinging Rebound - Your shot rebounds savagely into you; take 3d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"DGA38Fky2cV8JTgQ","type":0,"text":"Blinded - A backlash of string and splinters blinds you until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":1}}},{"_id":"7ABCIBFupULahEDz","type":0,"text":"Incapacitated - Your fumble leaves you reeling; you are incapacitated until the start of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"incapacitated","duration":1}}},{"_id":"57JMBkJu927qoY8n","type":0,"text":"Devastating Rebound - Your projectile rebounds catastrophically into you; take 4d8 damage.","img":"icons/svg/blood.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4d8","damageType":"weapon"}}},{"_id":"stB5AIue9VYXx4nJ","type":0,"text":"Pulled Muscle - You tear something deep inside; you gain one level of exhaustion until you recover.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"SNH9bbdWWMrP4Z42","type":0,"text":"Wild Ricochet - Your shot ricochets wildly toward the nearest ally; roll an attack against their AC.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"ranged","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392749,"modifiedTime":1783703392749,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"e3vBOe1743ljlJUz","name":"Tier 4 Spell Critical Hits (Levels 13-20)","description":"Critical hit effects for spell attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Legendary effects for legendary adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"grZofcvtBC0iCmt9","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your critical spell deals damage as normal, but no additional effect occurs.","img":"icons/svg/d20-highlight.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"d1pmS1V4PDkCH1N5","type":0,"text":"Sluggish Mind - The target's thoughts turn to sludge, giving them disadvantage on saving throws until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Sluggish Mind","duration":1}}},{"_id":"5tQ6iv3jNPc68Gry","type":0,"text":"Hex of Frailty - A hex of frailty erodes the target's defenses, giving them a -2 penalty to AC until removed.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":-1}}},{"_id":"PnGHOzeL5T9w52zK","type":0,"text":"Searing Flash - A blinding burst of arcane light sears the target's eyes, leaving them blinded until the end of their next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"k3bfULpTe8vUDCOm","type":0,"text":"Magic Disruption - Your spell disrupts the target's magic. They have disadvantage on spell attacks and saves for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/silenced.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak","save.all"],"effectName":"Magic Disruption","duration":3}}},{"_id":"HX2e20MqIPxnMKQL","type":0,"text":"Mana Burn - Raw magic ignites the target's own reserves, dealing 2d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"qcOdkPe9mGghzPfh","type":0,"text":"Withering Curse - A withering hex corrodes the target from within; they must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be poisoned.","img":"icons/svg/poison.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"poisoned"}}},{"_id":"vhQfQAffRT0ikVd8","type":0,"text":"Concussive Blast - A concussive shockwave hammers the target; they must succeed on a DC 17 Strength save or be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"prone"}}},{"_id":"oYLYhSix3RRr1ryG","type":0,"text":"Arcane Annihilation - Magical fire engulfs the target. They take 3d8 fire damage at the start of each turn until Dispel Magic (DC 17) or similar.","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-yellow-orange.webp","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3S","damageType":"fire"}}},{"_id":"akZSKogqhTvX6Q40","type":0,"text":"Elemental Apocalypse - Your spell's element utterly overwhelms the target. Add 4d6 damage of the spell's type.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3S","damageType":"spell"}}},{"_id":"WeqwPEeDyZPWiA7n","type":0,"text":"Apocalyptic Blast - The force sends the target flying 60 feet, prone, stunned for 1 round, and takes 3d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/thrust.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"3S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"OQ0zhu6DxzxJZNNX","type":0,"text":"Numbing Frost - Creeping frost locks the target's limbs; they must succeed on a DC 17 Strength save or be restrained.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"str","effectCondition":"restrained"}}},{"_id":"EkPgdRZ7V0Z0jsNi","type":0,"text":"Mind Spike - A lance of psychic force stabs the target's mind; they must succeed on a DC 17 Wisdom save or be frightened of you.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"wis","effectCondition":"frightened"}}},{"_id":"CaaApsBFme0u4dQC","type":0,"text":"Overwhelming Arcane Power - Your devastating spell deals an additional 5d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"4S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"Yy8pXbeiV29kOcxO","type":0,"text":"Terrifying Magic - Your devastating spell terrifies the target to their core. They are frightened of you for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"frightened","duration":3}}},{"_id":"Zs84lAweYYbyuG4w","type":0,"text":"Arcane Vulnerability - Your magic leaves the target utterly exposed. Attacks against them have advantage for 3 rounds.","img":"icons/svg/target.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Arcane Vulnerability","duration":3}}},{"_id":"5iGhNtu7VjyfmlZn","type":0,"text":"Soulscored - The spell scars the target's very soul, inflicting one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"xJuc4flTQ54biWYd","type":0,"text":"Soul Rending - If target has 50 HP or fewer, they must make a DC 17 Wisdom save or take 6d10 force extra damage.","img":"icons/svg/skull.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"wis","damageFormula":"6d10","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"QfQvWKQOg481Prw9","type":0,"text":"Arcane Lock - Binding sigils seize the target's body; they must succeed on a DC 17 Constitution save or be paralyzed.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","effectCondition":"paralyzed"}}},{"_id":"uLndNqid1fPS6RWp","type":0,"text":"Elemental Detonation - The spell's energy detonates catastrophically, dealing bonus damage equal to the spell's slot-scaled magnitude.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1SB","damageType":"spell"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"crit"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392749,"modifiedTime":1783703392749,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}
{"_id":"2YTj1ZNDMwosHzWV","name":"Tier 4 Spell Fumbles (Levels 13-20)","description":"Fumble effects for spell attacks at Tier 4 (Levels 13-20). Effects are legendary for master adventurers.","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-fireball-smoke-strong-orange.webp","formula":"1d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"results":[{"_id":"8w2W8BiqiKXO4fIU","type":0,"text":"Nothing Special - Your spell fizzles harmlessly with no additional penalty.","img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","weight":6,"range":[1,6],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"none"}}},{"_id":"2sxcxzvsXwQkosqT","type":0,"text":"Grounded Magic - Your spell earths itself through your body. You have disadvantage on attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":8,"range":[7,14],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Grounded Magic","duration":1}}},{"_id":"4KuppQKEfJc6Fg3n","type":0,"text":"Spell Recoil - The spell lashes back as it leaves you. You have disadvantage on your next ranged spell attack.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":8,"range":[15,22],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"attack.rsak","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Spell Recoil","duration":0}}},{"_id":"34EzfJOomZbx1OyB","type":0,"text":"Arcane Hiccup - Your magic stutters and misfires. You have disadvantage on spell attacks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":7,"range":[23,29],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":["attack.msak","attack.rsak"],"advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Arcane Hiccup","duration":1}}},{"_id":"rqK75Dln4xoU8PYI","type":0,"text":"Somatic Cramp - Your casting hand cramps violently. You have disadvantage on concentration checks until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":7,"range":[30,36],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"disadvantage","advantageScope":"concentration","advantageTarget":"self","effectName":"Somatic Cramp","duration":1}}},{"_id":"whFvnPaU8uyCzvbK","type":0,"text":"Arcane Backlash - Raw magic rebounds into you. Take force damage equal to one of the spell's damage dice.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":6,"range":[37,42],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1S","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"NiwtWHEk5ZtCIPx1","type":0,"text":"Component Combustion - Your material components ignite in your grip. Take 1d6 fire damage.","img":"icons/svg/fire.svg","weight":6,"range":[43,48],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d6","damageType":"fire"}}},{"_id":"hyS2GoMrUIBdgS21","type":0,"text":"Telegraphed Magic - Your fumbled casting tips your hand. Enemies have advantage on their next saving throw against your spells.","img":"icons/svg/daze.svg","weight":6,"range":[49,54],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"save.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Telegraphed Magic","duration":0}}},{"_id":"96tsc6b6xsWVsggB","type":0,"text":"Exposed Weave - Your botched weave leaves you unguarded. Attacks against you have advantage until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[55,59],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"advantage","advantageScope":"attack.all","advantageTarget":"grants","effectName":"Exposed Weave","duration":1}}},{"_id":"GLbiAzkElZRD562v","type":0,"text":"Warped Focus - The recoil throws off your aim. You take a -2 penalty to attack rolls until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":5,"range":[60,64],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"attack","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"Yuc9OKr6Qjpiw9BZ","type":0,"text":"Shattered Wards - The backlash shreds your protective wards. You take a -2 penalty to AC until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/hazard.svg","weight":5,"range":[65,69],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"penalty","penaltyType":"ac","penaltyValue":-2,"duration":1}}},{"_id":"QNqUvnxjSadsRdiV","type":0,"text":"Backlash Sprawl - The detonation throws you off your feet. You are knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":5,"range":[70,74],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"prone","duration":0}}},{"_id":"iKT1JT7RjCOVcTcv","type":0,"text":"Magical Backlash - The spell's energy rebounds painfully. Take 1d8 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":5,"range":[75,79],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d8","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"bNazvpTga6dU2yR6","type":0,"text":"Blinding Feedback - A blinding flash of misfired magic sears your eyes. You are blinded until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/blind.svg","weight":4,"range":[80,83],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"blinded","duration":0}}},{"_id":"6ScsnRkSzzMAdmqi","type":0,"text":"Searing Recoil - Searing magical energy tears back into you. Take 1d10 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/lightning.svg","weight":4,"range":[84,87],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"1d10","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"Is8NEsPtSv3VJKuH","type":0,"text":"Catastrophic Rebound - Your spell collapses inward. Make a DC 17 Constitution saving throw or take 5d6 force damage and be knocked prone.","img":"icons/svg/terror.svg","weight":4,"range":[88,91],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"save","saveDC":17,"saveAbility":"con","damageFormula":"5d6","damageType":"force","effectCondition":"prone","failEffect":"Take force damage and be knocked prone"}}},{"_id":"g9POQnwfAWmqiCbG","type":0,"text":"Feedback Stun - Arcane feedback locks every muscle rigid. You are stunned until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/paralysis.svg","weight":3,"range":[92,94],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"stunned","duration":0}}},{"_id":"ci6sPLcm5ZYxxVRX","type":0,"text":"Mana Drain - The failed casting rips the vigor from you. You gain one level of exhaustion.","img":"icons/svg/downgrade.svg","weight":3,"range":[95,97],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"condition","effectCondition":"exhaustion","duration":-1}}},{"_id":"4YQfsrt5TXINvAqi","type":0,"text":"Wild Surge Jolt - Wild magic detonates through your body. Take 2d6 force damage.","img":"icons/svg/explosion.svg","weight":2,"range":[98,99],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"damage","damageFormula":"2d6","damageType":"force"}}},{"_id":"m8XjmJJCPqyvjM9b","type":0,"text":"Misfired Blast - Your spell veers wildly and misfires at the nearest ally. Make a spell attack against the nearest ally; on a hit, they take the spell's damage.","img":"icons/svg/combat.svg","weight":1,"range":[100,100],"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"drawn":false,"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"effectType":"attackAlly"}}}],"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"flags":{"dorman-lakelys-crit-fumble-tables":{"tier":4,"attackType":"spell","resultType":"fumble"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"4.0.0","coreVersion":"13.0","createdTime":1783703392749,"modifiedTime":1783703392749,"lastModifiedBy":"build-script"}}